Task 4
Consider this function that prints a page number on the left or
right side of a page:
if page % 2 == 0:
print(page)
else:
print("%60s%d" % (" ", page))
Introduce a function that returns a Boolean to make the
condition in the if statement easier to understand.
if page % 2 == 0:
    print (page)
    else:
        print("%60s%d" % (" ", page))

